Name: Baby Bee
About the game: Guide Baby Bee through beautiful locations on a quest to get all the flowers with the minimum effort. Earn stars to make new bees and unlock levels and accessories! Embark on an epic journey through the awesome vastness of nature! Meet crazy characters in your journey, find out if they are friend or foe! Baby Bee introduces an original game play dynamic with a simple set of rules that evolves into increasingly complex puzzles. An experience that is easy for a child to understand but challenging even for a rocket scientist to solve.
